# 🚀 Dockerized Strapi + PostgreSQL + Nginx

This project sets up a full Docker environment for **Strapi** (a Node.js-based headless CMS), **PostgreSQL** (database), and **Nginx** (reverse proxy), allowing you to access the Strapi admin panel at **http://localhost**.

---

## 📦 Stack Used

- **Strapi** – CMS (port: 1337 internally)
- **PostgreSQL** – DB (port: 5432)
- **Nginx** – Reverse Proxy (exposes Strapi on port: 80)
- **Docker & Docker Compose**

---

## 📁 Directory Structure

my-project/
├── Dockerfile
├── docker-compose.yml
├── nginx/
│ └── default.conf
├── package.json
└── (Your Strapi App Files)


---

